Pre-Game Insights: Gareth Southgate’s side face Switzerland today (Saturday) in the quarter-finals.
Southgate trusts his favourite players to get the job done, although he was very impressed with how all his subs did in extra time against Slovakia!
Post-Match Reflections: It might also be the end of Gareth Southgate as England’s manager, which would make people very sad too, because he’s done such a good job over the last eight years.
